release.changelog: Neptune is getting a brand new start page with shortcut support in this update. The shortcuts on the home screen will work independently of your bookmarks list. If you want to set a custom homepage instead of the start page, you can change this option in the app settings. Additionally, we have updated the address and search bar with the latest generation of Android tools.
